Presentation

tex-templates is a collection of LaTeX styles for different usages.

Slides

tex-templates provides styles for creating slides with the Beamer tool.
- CIAD Laboratory located at the Université de Technologie de
Belfort-Montbéliard and the Université Bourgogne Europe
“[download]”:./presentations/ciad-2025

PhD Theses

tex-templates provides the official styles for writing a PhD thesis in
the following Universities:

- Université de Technologie de Belfort-Montbéliard [download part 1]
[download part 2] [download part 3]

- Université Bourgogne Europe [download part 1] [download part 2]
[download part 3]
- Université Marie et Louis Pasteur [download part 1] [download part 2]
[download part 3]

Examples for these PhD thesis styles may be found at:
http://www.ciad-lab.fr/

French Research Supervision Accreditation

tex-templates provides the unofficial styles for preparing a French
Research Supervision Accredidation (In French: Habilitation à diriger
des rerchers - HDR):

- Application document for Université Bourgogne Europe [download part 1]
[download part 2] [download part 3]
- HDR report for Université Bourgogne Europe [download part 1] [download
part 2] [download part 3]

Technical Reports

tex-templates provides the styles for writing the technical reports of
the CIAD Laboratory at the Université de Technologie de
Belfort-Montbéliard

- Technical or Scientific report style
“[download]”:./reports/utbmciad-2025

Conference Papers

tex-templates provides the styles for the following conferences:
- IngéDoc at the Université de Technologie de Belfort-Montbéliard
“[download]”:./papers/ingedoc

Installation

1.  For the reports, install the tex-upmethodology collection of
    packages (also available on CTAN, and included in the major TeX
    distributions)
2.  Copy the content of the current directory inside one of your texmf
    directory, usually /usr/share/texmf/tex/latex/tex-templates or
    $HOME/.texmf on Unix operating systems.
3.  Update the LaTeX databases from the command line:

$> mktexlsr
$> update-updmap —quiet

